Paper: hep-th/9302102

Date: 1993-02-22

Title: Yangians and Gelfand-Zetlin bases

Comments: 14 pages

Journal-ref: Publ.Res.Inst.Math.Sci.Kyoto 30 (1994) 459-478

We establish a relationship between the modern theory of Yangians and theclassical construction of the Gelfand-Zetlin bases for the complex Lie algebra$\gn$. Our approach allows us to produce the $q$-analogues of theGelfand-Zetlin formulae in a straightforward way.